A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce; and for
2 other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, North Fulton is a diverse and thriving region boasting six unique cities; nearly
4 400,000 residents; six Fortune 500 companies; a highly educated workforce and talent base;
5 top-tier public and private educational institutions; world-class healthcare; nationally
6 acclaimed outdoor parkland, trails, and green space; a vibrant arts, culture, and entertainment
7 scene; and a quality of life that is second to none; and
8 WHEREAS, for over five decades, the Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce has
9 served as a catalyst for the region's growth, connectivity, innovation, transformation, and
10 economic vitality by serving as the voice and champion of business in North Fulton; and
11 WHEREAS, the Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce is a 5-Star Accredited
12 Chamber, and as the only regional chamber in North Fulton comprising six distinct cities, it
13 is uniquely positioned to bring industry leaders, entrepreneurs, and experts from surrounding
14 communities together, fostering innovation and collaboration; and
