15 WHEREAS, the Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce's over five decades of success
16 began in 1973 with a small group of local business leaders who, 20 years before GA-400 was
17 built, envisioned the potential for the region and invested in their community to ensure its
18 growth and prosperity; and
19 WHEREAS, the mission of the Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce is to grow
20 business, develop talent, and lead regional prosperity across North Fulton; and
21 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the Greater North Fulton Chamber of
22 Commerce receive the recognition of this body.
23 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
24 the members of this body recognize and commend the Greater North Fulton Chamber of
25 Commerce and extend best wishes for continued success.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
27 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
28 Greater North Fulton Chamber of Commerce.
